videos.description: LSU's Darius Days drains a shot from behind the arc while being fouled for a 4-point play.
videos.headline: LSU's Days sinks 3 while being fouled

videos.description: Kavell Bigby-Williams finds the rim for two slams on back-to-back possessions to narrow LSU's deficit vs. Tennessee.
videos.headline: Bigby-Williams slams it on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield sidesteps a 3-pointer to give him 25 points on the day.
videos.headline: Schofield drains 3 to continue hot night

videos.description: Grant Williams spins around a defender and scores on an and-1 to give Tennessee an 80-78 lead in OT.
videos.headline: Williams spins into rim to give Tennessee lead in OT

videos.description: Grant Williams fouls Ja'vonte Smart with 0.6 seconds left in OT, leading to Smart's free throws that seal LSU's 82-80 win over Tennessee.
videos.headline: Crucial OT foul leads to LSU defeating Tennessee

videos.description: Ja'vonte Smart scores 29 points and a last-second foul gives No. 13 LSU the deciding points in an 82-80 overtime victory over No. 5 Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (LSU squeaks by Tennessee for wild OT win) 2019/2/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: LSU squeaks by Tennessee for wild OT win
